lan MacNeill (spelled with two l's) has a traditional ancestral home on the island of Gigha."]}]},{"name":"NN","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Originally a pet form of   Ann   (for the initial <i>N-</i>,  compare  Ned  ). It is now also widely used as a short form of   Nancy ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"NN MacNeil was born about 1267. She had at least 1 daughter with Iye IV MacKay of Strathnaver."},"et":{"about 1267–":"umbes 1267–Surnud","1300–1370":"1300–1370","1351–1395":"1351–1395","1267–Female":"1267–Surnud","1267":"1267","1300":"1300","1351":"1351","1395":"1395","about 1267":"umbes 1267","1370":"1370","Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"about 1267–":"noin 1267–Kuollut","1300–1370":"1300–1370","1351–1395":"1351–1395","1267–Female":"1267–Kuollut","1267":"1267","1300":"1300","1351":"1351","1395":"1395","about 1267":"noin 1267","1370":"1370","Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland"},"fr":{"about 1267–":"environ 1267–Décédée","1300–1370":"1300–1370","1351–1395":"1351–1395","1267–Female":"1267–Décédée","1267":"1267","1300":"1300","1351":"1351","1395":"1395","about 1267":"environ 1267","1370":"1370","Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Glamis, Forfarshire, Écosse","lifeSummary":"NN MacNeil est née environ 1267. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Iye IV MacKay of Strathnaver."},"de":{"about 1267–":"um 1267–Verstorben","1300–1370":"1300–1370","1351–1395":"1351–1395","1267–Female":"1267–Verstorben","1267":"1267","1300":"1300","1351":"1351","1395":"1395","about 1267":"um 1267","1370":"1370","Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Glamis, Forfarshire, Scotland","lifeSummary":"NN MacNeil wurde um 1267 geboren. Sie hatte mit Iye IV MacKay of Strathnaver mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"about 1267–":"about 1267–Desede","1300–1370":"1300–1370","1351–1395":"1351–1395","1267–Female":"1267–Desede","1267":"1267","1300":"1300","1351":"1351","139